The new Star Wars TV show The Mandalorian follows the adventures of a ruthless bounty hunter named Din Djarin.
Geek’s Guide to the Galaxy host David Barr Kirtley says that’s appropriate, since the character is clearly intended to capitalize on the popularity of another Star Wars bounty hunter, Boba Fett.
